# 7. Decay Calculations

## Intrinsic Value

```python
def intrinsic_value(spot, strike, option_type):
    if option_type == "CE":
        return max(spot - strike, 0)
    elif option_type == "PE":
        return max(strike - spot, 0)
```

## Time Value

```python
def time_value(ltp, intrinsic):
    return max(ltp - intrinsic, 0)
```

## Approx Daily Decay

```python
def approx_daily_decay(time_value, dte):
    if dte <= 0:
        return time_value
    return time_value / dte
```

